#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "<h1 id=\"2fa\">Using <i>KeePassXC</i> as an authenticator app for two-factor authentication</h1>\n"
msgid "<h1 id=\"2fa\">Using <i>Secrets</i> as an authenticator app for two-factor authentication</h1>\n"
msgstr "<h1 id=\"2fa\">Verwendung von <i>KeePassXC</i> als Authenticator-App für die Zwei-Faktor-Authentifizierung</h1>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Many websites offer two-factor authentication as a safer method than using "
"just a password. For example, you can configure an authentication app, like "
"Google Authenticator, to generate a one-time code of 6 digits when signing "
"in to a website."
msgstr ""
"Viele Websites bieten die Zwei-Faktor-Authentifizierung als sicherere "
"Methode an als nur die Verwendung eines Passworts. Zum Beispiel können Sie "
"eine Authentifizierungs-App wie Google Authenticator einrichten, um einen "
"einmaligen Code von 6 Ziffern zu generieren, wenn Sie sich bei einer Website "
"anmelden."

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "You can use *KeePassXC* to generate such one-time codes in Tails. The\n"
#| "technology used to generate these codes is called [[!wikipedia time-based\n"
#| "one-time password]] (TOTP).\n"
msgid ""
"You can use *Secrets* to generate such one-time codes in Tails. The\n"
"technology used to generate these codes is called [[!wikipedia time-based\n"
"one-time password]] (TOTP).\n"
msgstr "Sie können *KeePassXC* verwenden, um solche einmaligen Codes in Tails zu generieren. Die Technologie, die zur Erzeugung dieser Codes verwendet wird, heißt [[!wikipedia_de Time-based one-time password desc=\"zeitbasiertes einmaliges Passwort\"]] (TOTP).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "To configure two-factor authentication for an entry in your *KeePassXC* "
#| "database:"
msgid ""
"To configure two-factor authentication for an entry in your password safe:"
msgstr ""
"Um die Zwei-Faktor-Authentifizierung für einen Eintrag in Ihrer *KeePassXC*-"
"Datenbank zu konfigurieren:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"From the website or application for which you are configuring two-factor "
"authentication, identify the *secret* that you need to generate the one-time "
"codes. This secret is a string of characters that is often provided together "
"with a QR code."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Click on the entry of your database for which you want to configure two-"
#| "factor authentication."
msgid ""
"In the *Secrets* password manager, select the entry of your safe for which "
"you want to configure two-factor authentication."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf den Eintrag Ihrer Datenbank, für den Sie die Zwei-Faktor-"
"Authentifizierung konfigurieren möchten."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "At the bottom of the right pane, select **Show More**."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the new options that appear, enter the secret from the website or "
"application in the **One-Time Password Secret** text box."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   A one-time code appears above the **One-Time Password Secret** text box.\n"
